videos.description: Cal caps off a 10-0 run with Jabari Bird finding Ivan Rabb with a dime for the layup.
videos.headline: Bird finds Rabb with a pretty pass for the layup

videos.description: Sam Singer extends Cal's run to 12-0 with a bank shot.
videos.headline: The bank is open for Singer

videos.description: Casey Benson splits the D with a bounce pass and Jordan Bell dunks it down to end Cal's run.
videos.headline: Bell punishes the rim with a huge dunk

videos.description: Jordan Bell finds Chris Boucher inside for the dunk and the foul. Can Oregon come back on the road?
videos.headline: Boucher throws down the and-1 dunk

videos.description: Jordan Bell turnover leads to fast break dunk for Jabari Bird.
videos.headline: Bird rocks the rim with a two-handed slam

videos.description: a Charlie Moore turnover leads to an open 3-pointer for Payton Pritchard. Oregon on a 9-0 run
videos.headline: Pritchard buries a 3-pointer from the wing

videos.description: Chris Boucher gets to the inside and scores to give Oregon their first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Boucher gets the tough layup to go

videos.description: Dillion Brooks gets the lucky bounce on his turnaround jumper. Can Oregon hang on for the win?
videos.headline: Brooks turnaround jumper rattles in

videos.description: After trailing by as much as 16 points, Oregon rallies back behind Dillon Brooks to stun Cal 68-65.
videos.headline: Brooks' 17-point 2nd half leads Oregon to stunning comeback win
